00:00:31.156 --> 00:00:33.575 position:50% align:center
saving your stuff at
the cost of your life.

00:00:33.658 --> 00:00:35.243 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF]
Yeah.

00:00:35.326 --> 00:00:36.327 position:50% align:center
Funny how now and then,

00:00:36.411 --> 00:00:39.539 position:50% align:center
it still feels like
God has my back.

00:00:42.292 --> 00:00:44.252 position:50% align:center
