00:00:46.963 --> 00:00:48.381 position:50% align:center
Prob'ly.

00:00:48.465 --> 00:00:55.055 position:50% align:center
[JOE, CHIEF laugh]

00:02:26.771 --> 00:02:30.692 position:50% align:center
[MARA]
Mio! Get back here!

00:02:30.775 --> 00:02:32.027 position:50% align:center
Hey!

00:02:34.529 --> 00:02:35.905 position:50% align:center
[MARA]
Mio!

00:02:37.157 --> 00:02:39.117 position:50% align:center
[MIO]
I lit the fire.

00:02:40.535 --> 00:02:42.370 position:50% align:center
I know I'm getting kicked out.

00:02:42.454 --> 00:02:45.915 position:50% align:center
Why waste our time
talking about it?

00:02:45.999 --> 00:02:47.417 position:50% align:center
It was you, right?

00:02:47.500 --> 00:02:50.253 position:50% align:center
You told Hikawa's goons
that Joe was here.

00:02:50.337 --> 00:02:52.505 position:50% align:center
[MIO] Hiding his identity
like a coward.

00:02:52.589 --> 00:02:55.008 position:50% align:center
You think you did something
brave? You know this is--

00:02:55.091 --> 00:02:56.426 position:50% align:center
[MIO]
I know what?

00:02:56.509 --> 00:02:58.636 position:50% align:center
I didn't even ask to
come to this country.

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:01.139 position:50% align:center
You dragged me!

00:03:01.222 --> 00:03:03.058 position:50% align:center
If we'd just stayed where
we were and got killed,

00:03:03.141 --> 00:03:06.311 position:50% align:center
at least by now we'd be done
with all the bullshit!

00:03:07.979 --> 00:03:09.189 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:03:11.608 --> 00:03:13.943 position:50% align:center
Now, niÃ±o, no matter
how bad it gets,

00:03:14.027 --> 00:03:16.529 position:50% align:center
as long as you're alive,
it can get better.

00:03:16.613 --> 00:03:19.991 position:50% align:center
The fire's out and nobody
got hurt. Let's talk.

00:03:20.075 --> 00:03:22.285 position:50% align:center
Nah, let's not.
I've heard it all.

00:03:22.369 --> 00:03:23.870 position:50% align:center
None of that shit
you go on about

00:03:23.953 --> 00:03:26.414 position:50% align:center
is ever gonna happen, old man.

00:03:26.498 --> 00:03:28.708 position:50% align:center
But if I keep fighting
for it, it might.

00:03:28.792 --> 00:03:30.210 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:03:30.293 --> 00:03:32.253 position:50% align:center
Maybe if you knew when
to quit fighting,

00:03:32.337 --> 00:03:34.464 position:50% align:center
your kid would be alive!

00:03:35.590 --> 00:03:39.511 position:50% align:center
Now Pops is dead and
it's all because of you!

00:03:39.594 --> 00:03:41.513 position:50% align:center
[MARA]
Mio!

00:03:41.596 --> 00:03:43.348 position:50% align:center
Watch your mouth!

00:04:06.329 --> 00:04:07.956 position:50% align:center
You're not gonna stop me, man.

00:04:08.039 --> 00:04:09.708 position:50% align:center
Didn't plan to.

00:04:09.791 --> 00:04:12.919 position:50% align:center
But if you run away now,
you're gonna regret it.

00:04:13.003 --> 00:04:14.421 position:50% align:center
You know this is your fault.

00:04:14.504 --> 00:04:16.548 position:50% align:center
It happened 'cause
you showed up.

00:04:16.631 --> 00:04:20.301 position:50% align:center
Maybe you should blame the kid
who ran off with my bike.

00:04:22.721 --> 00:04:25.849 position:50% align:center
You wanna know how
it ends, don't you?

00:04:25.932 --> 00:04:29.894 position:50% align:center
Man, it's already over.
It's been over.

00:04:38.528 --> 00:04:40.947 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF]
Hey, Carlo.

00:04:41.031 --> 00:04:44.242 position:50% align:center
I hope you're being
good for your mother.

00:04:44.325 --> 00:04:47.203 position:50% align:center
I thought I'd figured out
the way to move forward,

00:04:47.287 --> 00:04:50.248 position:50% align:center
but now, I don't know if leaving
the old country with you

00:04:50.331 --> 00:04:51.875 position:50% align:center
was the right move,

00:04:51.958 --> 00:04:56.296 position:50% align:center
and maybe I'm a fool for still
trying to make my home here.

00:05:00.050 --> 00:05:01.384 position:50% align:center
Carlo.

00:05:01.468 --> 00:05:05.180 position:50% align:center
Your old man kept me alive,
the way you did for him,

00:05:05.263 --> 00:05:06.806 position:50% align:center
so thanks.

00:05:08.641 --> 00:05:10.977 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF]
I told you to wait in the car.

00:05:11.061 --> 00:05:13.063 position:50% align:center
[JOE] This is the time
for me to pick you up.

00:05:13.146 --> 00:05:14.439 position:50% align:center
I'm your second, right?

00:05:14.522 --> 00:05:16.483 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF chuckles]

00:05:17.525 --> 00:05:19.194 position:50% align:center
You're feeling weak
in the knees,

00:05:19.277 --> 00:05:21.488 position:50% align:center
but we're still in the fight.

00:05:22.572 --> 00:05:24.908 position:50% align:center
And it's not just
you and me now.

00:05:24.991 --> 00:05:26.785 position:50% align:center
We're all in this together.

00:05:26.868 --> 00:05:30.580 position:50% align:center
He was the first one
to share my dream.

00:05:30.663 --> 00:05:34.250 position:50% align:center
Just wish he'd had the chance
to see it come true.

00:05:35.293 --> 00:05:38.755 position:50% align:center
You'd best make your way
home when this is over.

00:05:38.838 --> 00:05:42.384 position:50% align:center
Whether they welcome
you back or not.

00:05:42.467 --> 00:05:44.302 position:50% align:center
[horn honking]

00:05:44.386 --> 00:05:46.721 position:50% align:center
[MARA]
C'mon, guys, we gotta go.

00:05:56.648 --> 00:05:57.691 position:50% align:center
What is that?

00:05:57.774 --> 00:05:59.859 position:50% align:center
You always do it
before your fights.

00:05:59.943 --> 00:06:02.612 position:50% align:center
Something from the old country.

00:06:02.696 --> 00:06:06.616 position:50% align:center
That was my way of telling them
I wanna make it back safe.

00:06:06.700 --> 00:06:08.118 position:50% align:center
C'mon.

00:06:18.878 --> 00:06:21.047 position:50% align:center
[MASUDA] This is an
issue, Mister. Hikawa.

00:06:21.131 --> 00:06:22.966 position:50% align:center
I have no objection
to a potential buyer

00:06:23.049 --> 00:06:24.426 position:50% align:center
