00:06:24.509 --> 00:06:26.344 position:50% align:center
That stops short of arson.

00:06:26.428 --> 00:06:28.096 position:50% align:center
Kids these days, am I right?

00:06:28.179 --> 00:06:30.015 position:50% align:center
