to set it on fire.

00:06:34.602 --> 00:06:38.064 position:50% align:center
[HIKAWA] In any case, clearing
them out is best for us both.

00:06:38.148 --> 00:06:39.774 position:50% align:center
Once the immigrant camp is gone,

00:06:39.858 --> 00:06:41.818 position:50% align:center
