and I get the land.

00:06:41.901 --> 00:06:44.362 position:50% align:center
That was what we
agreed to, after all.

00:06:44.446 --> 00:06:45.905 position:50% align:center
Assuming they're gone.

00:06:45.989 --> 00:06:47.699 position:50% align:center
No need to worry yourself.

00:06:47.782 --> 00:06:49.200 position:50% align:center
You should come out
to the fight tonight

00:06:49.284 --> 00:06:52.162 position:50% align:center
and watch my boy Mamiya
destroy that bum.

00:06:52.245 --> 00:06:55.165 position:50% align:center
[MASUDA] Either way,
I've got nothing to worry about.

00:06:55.248 --> 00:06:57.459 position:50% align:center
I'll deal with whomever can pay.

00:06:57.542 --> 00:07:00.211 position:50% align:center
Could be you or them.

00:07:01.963 --> 00:07:04.716 position:50% align:center
So, I will not be
sitting with you,

00:07:04.799 --> 00:07:06.926 position:50% align:center
but I will be watching.

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:16.603 position:50% align:center
[HIKAWA]
Tch.

00:07:16.686 --> 00:07:19.564 position:50% align:center
You wanna talk down
to me, you prick?

00:07:19.647 --> 00:07:21.524 position:50% align:center
But some fellas never
learn to shut up

00:07:21.608 --> 00:07:24.611 position:50% align:center
until someone feeds
'em their teeth.

00:07:27.530 --> 00:07:30.533 position:50% align:center
[ANNOUNCER A] Whose soul will
be dragged to hell tonight?

00:07:30.617 --> 00:07:32.452 position:50% align:center
