change forever?

00:07:59.938 --> 00:08:01.272 position:50% align:center
[MAMIYA]
Hmph.

00:08:04.442 --> 00:08:06.319 position:50% align:center
Yeah, Mamiya! Kick his ass!

00:08:06.403 --> 00:08:07.904 position:50% align:center
You got a problem
with our country,

00:08:07.987 --> 00:08:10.281 position:50% align:center
