from the outside.

00:09:16.556 --> 00:09:18.600 position:50% align:center
You're winning!

00:09:18.683 --> 00:09:21.144 position:50% align:center
Is that how they do
things back home?

00:09:21.227 --> 00:09:22.645 position:50% align:center
In your rat hole?

00:09:22.729 --> 00:09:24.397 position:50% align:center
[growls]

00:09:35.116 --> 00:09:36.743 position:50% align:center
[REF A]
Down!

00:09:36.826 --> 00:09:43.375 position:50% align:center
One! Two! Three! Four!

00:09:43.458 --> 00:09:49.964 position:50% align:center
Five! Six! Seven! Eight!

00:09:57.764 --> 00:10:02.394 position:50% align:center
