as you're getting' older.

00:10:05.563 --> 00:10:08.108 position:50% align:center
You don't look a day
over 50, Chief.

00:10:08.191 --> 00:10:09.776 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF chuckles]

00:10:13.321 --> 00:10:15.156 position:50% align:center
[JOE]
Get home safe.

00:10:17.492 --> 00:10:19.828 position:50% align:center
[JOE]
That's why you're here, right?

00:10:19.911 --> 00:10:21.830 position:50% align:center
Think of your home.

00:10:40.765 --> 00:10:42.434 position:50% align:center
Lemme tell ya,
it takes some balls,

00:10:42.517 --> 00:10:44.561 position:50% align:center
