00:10:45.979 --> 00:10:48.273 position:50% align:center
what you were runnin'
away from, now do I?

00:10:48.356 --> 00:10:52.027 position:50% align:center
We all wanna choose where
we live and where we die.

00:11:00.827 --> 00:11:01.995 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:03.997 --> 00:11:05.957 position:50% align:center
