my dream come true, right?

00:11:15.091 --> 00:11:16.718 position:50% align:center
Well, you get what you pay for,

00:11:16.801 --> 00:11:18.678 position:50% align:center
but I guess when your
dreams don't come true,

00:11:18.762 --> 00:11:21.473 position:50% align:center
