everything on God.

00:11:21.556 --> 00:11:24.392 position:50% align:center
The hummingbirds don't
connect us to God.

00:11:24.476 --> 00:11:27.145 position:50% align:center
They connect us to our homeland.

00:11:27.228 --> 00:11:30.315 position:50% align:center
If we ever lose our way in life,
these birds remind us

00:11:30.398 --> 00:11:32.609 position:50% align:center
that we still have a
place to go back to.

00:11:32.692 --> 00:11:34.861 position:50% align:center
[MIO] You always say this
crap like you believe it.

00:11:34.944 --> 00:11:37.072 position:50% align:center
I'm almost impressed.

00:11:37.155 --> 00:11:38.490 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:41.076 --> 00:11:42.911 position:50% align:center
Hey, man, pull over at
the next rest stop.

00:11:42.994 --> 00:11:44.829 position:50% align:center
Hot damn, I was
waitin' for that.

00:11:44.913 --> 00:11:47.540 position:50% align:center
