the john, or what?

00:11:49.834 --> 00:11:52.087 position:50% align:center
[MIO] You're gonna let me
out and keep going.

00:11:52.170 --> 00:11:53.713 position:50% align:center
Hell, that's simple enough.

00:11:53.797 --> 00:11:56.841 position:50% align:center
Let you out and keep
goin', huh? Easy.

00:11:56.925 --> 00:11:58.343 position:50% align:center
We're cool.

00:12:01.971 --> 00:12:05.100 position:50% align:center
[JOE] Stand your ground!
Come around from the side!

00:12:07.352 --> 00:12:09.437 position:50% align:center
[JOE] Good! Don't attack
down the middle!

00:12:09.521 --> 00:12:10.355 position:50% align:center
That's the way, Chief!

00:12:10.438 --> 00:12:12.691 position:50% align:center
Show this punk how it's done!

00:12:14.317 --> 00:12:16.111 position:50% align:center
[REF A]
Down!

00:12:16.194 --> 00:12:20.949 position:50% align:center
One! Two! Three!

00:12:21.032 --> 00:12:24.285 position:50% align:center
Four! Five!

00:12:31.626 --> 00:12:33.128 position:50% align:center
