one point deducted.

00:12:42.095 --> 00:12:43.388 position:50% align:center
[JOE]
Chief!

00:12:46.016 --> 00:12:49.144 position:50% align:center
That's the fight, old man.

00:12:53.314 --> 00:12:58.028 position:50% align:center
I'm not done with
you, little boy.

00:12:58.111 --> 00:13:00.030 position:50% align:center
[buzzer sounds]

00:13:20.633 --> 00:13:24.721 position:50% align:center
[JOE] Look at him, Chief.
He's got nothin' left.

00:13:24.804 --> 00:13:27.182 position:50% align:center
It won't go past this round.

00:13:32.562 --> 00:13:34.814 position:50% align:center
Hey, Chief?

00:13:34.898 --> 00:13:36.399 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I'm with you.

00:13:36.483 --> 00:13:41.988 position:50% align:center
That light I saw in you
back then, you see it in me?

00:13:42.072 --> 00:13:44.824 position:50% align:center
If you want your
answer, listen to them.

00:13:44.908 --> 00:13:50.914 position:50% align:center
[IMMIGRANTS]
Go Chief! Go Chief! Go Chief...!

00:14:01.966 --> 00:14:03.885 position:50% align:center
