Joe.

00:14:03.968 --> 00:14:08.014 position:50% align:center
If I win this fight, I want
you to make me a promise.

00:14:08.098 --> 00:14:10.016 position:50% align:center
That you'll listen
to your heart,

00:14:10.100 --> 00:14:13.228 position:50% align:center
and you'll follow it
wherever it leads you.

00:14:14.521 --> 00:14:16.898 position:50% align:center
I'm holding you to it.

00:14:31.162 --> 00:14:33.289 position:50% align:center
He knows his job.

00:14:35.458 --> 00:14:39.254 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF]
Carlo, you watching?

00:14:39.337 --> 00:14:40.880 position:50% align:center
Chief!

00:14:54.686 --> 00:14:55.687 position:50% align:center
[CROWD cheers]

00:14:55.770 --> 00:14:57.647 position:50% align:center
