He's down!

00:14:57.731 --> 00:15:02.569 position:50% align:center
One! Two! Three!

00:15:02.652 --> 00:15:10.827 position:50% align:center
[REF A, CROWD] Four! Five!
Six! Seven! Eight...!

00:15:10.910 --> 00:15:12.245 position:50% align:center
Yeah, nine!

00:15:12.328 --> 00:15:13.955 position:50% align:center
[REF A, CROWD]
Ten!

00:15:15.290 --> 00:15:19.210 position:50% align:center
[REF A] The winner, by knockout
in the fifth round: Chief!

00:15:19.294 --> 00:15:22.505 position:50% align:center
[CROWD cheering]

00:15:22.589 --> 00:15:24.549 position:50% align:center
[growls]

00:15:24.632 --> 00:15:26.092 position:50% align:center
Shit!

00:15:28.595 --> 00:15:30.013 position:50% align:center
Well, go catch it!

00:15:30.096 --> 00:15:32.932 position:50% align:center
What the hell do you think
I'm paying you for, numbnuts?

00:15:33.016 --> 00:15:34.684 position:50% align:center
You too, ya little cretins!

00:15:34.768 --> 00:15:36.102 position:50% align:center
[MEN]
Uh. Sir!

00:15:36.186 --> 00:15:38.104 position:50% align:center
[HIKAWA]
Move it, ya bums!

00:15:39.898 --> 00:15:42.984 position:50% align:center
[REF A] The man from a distant
land who dominated the bracket,

00:15:43.068 --> 00:15:48.281 position:50% align:center
