[CHIEF]
Come on now, Mara.

00:16:05.715 --> 00:16:09.302 position:50% align:center
One drink's not
gonna hurt, is it?

00:16:09.386 --> 00:16:12.764 position:50% align:center
You'll be okay with water
for just one more night.

00:16:13.807 --> 00:16:17.977 position:50% align:center
Ha. Fine. By the way...

00:16:18.061 --> 00:16:20.480 position:50% align:center
...could you look
after it for me?

00:16:21.606 --> 00:16:24.067 position:50% align:center
Been saving it up
for some time now.

00:16:24.150 --> 00:16:28.279 position:50% align:center
Doin' it like this spares me
a load of paperwork, y'know?

00:16:32.450 --> 00:16:35.036 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I can lock it in the safe.

00:16:37.580 --> 00:16:40.959 position:50% align:center
You're the reason
all this is happening.

00:16:41.042 --> 00:16:43.086 position:50% align:center
I can't take credit.

00:16:43.169 --> 00:16:45.880 position:50% align:center
It's happening 'cause
you fought for it.

00:16:47.048 --> 00:16:49.217 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF]
Dreams change people.

00:16:49.300 --> 00:16:52.053 position:50% align:center
Not just the ones who're
havin' 'em either

00:16:52.137 --> 00:16:56.725 position:50% align:center
'cause those people have a way
of pullin' in others around 'em.

00:16:56.808 --> 00:17:00.353 position:50% align:center
You're the one who got me
chasing this dream, Joe,

00:17:00.437 --> 00:17:04.607 position:50% align:center
and I'm going to keep dreaming
it for as long as I can.

00:17:04.691 --> 00:17:08.528 position:50% align:center
And I still plan on holding you
to that promise you made me.

00:17:10.613 --> 00:17:13.742 position:50% align:center
Yeah. No more running.

00:17:17.912 --> 00:17:20.623 position:50% align:center
[SHIGA] Wait, you're saying
you're done with us?

00:17:20.707 --> 00:17:22.959 position:50% align:center
The only reason we let you hang
with us in the first place

00:17:23.043 --> 00:17:24.586 position:50% align:center
is 'cause we felt sorry for you!

00:17:24.669 --> 00:17:25.378 position:50% align:center
Didn't we?

00:17:25.462 --> 00:17:27.172 position:50% align:center
Oh, right. Yeah.

00:17:27.255 --> 00:17:31.134 position:50% align:center
I don't want pity, and I
don't wanna be like y'all.

00:17:31.217 --> 00:17:32.802 position:50% align:center
I'd rather be alone.

00:17:32.886 --> 00:17:35.221 position:50% align:center
Don't act like it wasn't
fun for you, too!

00:17:35.305 --> 00:17:38.808 position:50% align:center
No. It was really fun and easy.

00:17:38.892 --> 00:17:41.311 position:50% align:center
I could just let
myself be a loser.

00:17:41.394 --> 00:17:43.688 position:50% align:center
That's all I've been
doin' the whole time.

00:17:43.772 --> 00:17:46.399 position:50% align:center
I can't act like I'm
better than y'all.

00:17:48.777 --> 00:17:50.820 position:50% align:center
But I can be better if I stay.

00:17:50.904 --> 00:17:53.823 position:50% align:center
Ha! Now you're tryin' to
play the good guy, Mio?

00:17:53.907 --> 00:17:56.326 position:50% align:center
Hurry up and say
somethin', Bertie!

00:17:59.871 --> 00:18:03.041 position:50% align:center
Get that haircut fixed, bro,
'cause it's straight trash.

00:18:03.124 --> 00:18:04.584 position:50% align:center
Heard.

00:18:07.087 --> 00:18:09.047 position:50% align:center
Yo! This kid stabs
us in the back

00:18:09.130 --> 00:18:12.092 position:50% align:center
and you're just gonna roast
his haircut and walk away?

00:18:13.885 --> 00:18:17.180 position:50% align:center
[SHIGA]
Hey, slow down! What the hell?

00:18:19.766 --> 00:18:22.686 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF]
Nice breeze, huh?

00:18:22.769 --> 00:18:25.897 position:50% align:center
I'm thinkin' I'll hit
the road in the morning.

00:18:25.980 --> 00:18:28.149 position:50% align:center
Let Mara feed you
breakfast, first.

00:18:28.233 --> 00:18:29.609 position:50% align:center
Right.

00:18:31.986 --> 00:18:33.571 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF]
Hey, Joe?

00:18:33.655 --> 00:18:35.031 position:50% align:center
[JOE]
Hm?

00:18:36.241 --> 00:18:38.702 position:50% align:center
I'm afraid to fall asleep.

00:18:40.662 --> 00:18:41.996 position:50% align:center
I can't shake it.

00:18:42.080 --> 00:18:45.333 position:50% align:center
What if I wake up and
find out I dreamed it all?

00:18:45.417 --> 00:18:48.128 position:50% align:center
[BOTH laugh]

00:18:48.211 --> 00:18:49.838 position:50% align:center
I'm good from here.

00:18:49.921 --> 00:18:53.508 position:50% align:center
Could you let 'em know that
I've turned in for the night?

00:18:53.591 --> 00:18:56.553 position:50% align:center
I owe you. Thanks, Chief.

00:18:57.887 --> 00:19:00.098 position:50% align:center
[CHIEF chuckles]

00:19:01.224 --> 00:19:03.560 position:50% align:center
You don't owe me a single thing.

00:19:03.643 --> 00:19:07.772 position:50% align:center
We're family. It's what we do.

00:19:07.856 --> 00:19:09.315 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:19:10.358 --> 00:19:11.985 position:50% align:center
I'll see you bright and early.

00:19:12.068 --> 00:19:13.403 position:50% align:center
Right.

00:19:16.698 --> 00:19:20.952 position:50% align:center
And don't forget, you'll
always be our champion.

00:19:23.663 --> 00:19:27.834 position:50% align:center
Someday down the line,
I hope we face off again.

00:19:27.917 --> 00:19:30.503 position:50% align:center
A real match this time.

00:19:33.423 --> 00:19:34.924 position:50% align:center
[IMMIGRANT A] Son,
what'd they do to your hair?

00:19:35.008 --> 00:19:35.967 position:50% align:center
Bite me, pops.

00:19:36.051 --> 00:19:39.179 position:50% align:center
[ALL laughing]

00:19:51.524 --> 00:19:53.777 position:50% align:center
<i>Buenas noches.</i>

00:20:05.830 --> 00:20:07.332 position:50% align:center
[MIO]
Breakfast is ready, Joe.

00:20:07.415 --> 00:20:09.959 position:50% align:center
I'm gonna go get Chief--
you can head in whenever.

00:20:10.043 --> 00:20:12.754 position:50% align:center
Got it.

00:20:12.837 --> 00:20:14.339 position:50% align:center
Man, this is a spread.

00:20:14.422 --> 00:20:16.591 position:50% align:center
[MARA] You and Chief
both had a hard fight.

00:20:16.675 --> 00:20:18.843 position:50% align:center
Gotta get back some
of that energy.

00:20:18.927 --> 00:20:21.471 position:50% align:center
This is how you
keep a man strong!

00:20:21.554 --> 00:20:23.556 position:50% align:center
And the soup's got a truckload
of garlic in it, so you know--

00:20:23.640 --> 00:20:25.600 position:50% align:center
[MIO]
Mom, get out here!

00:20:25.684 --> 00:20:27.310 position:50% align:center
Mom!

00:20:30.689 --> 00:20:34.317 position:50% align:center
[MIO crying]

00:20:34.401 --> 00:20:35.944 position:50% align:center
[MARA]
How?

00:20:49.958 --> 00:20:54.963 position:50% align:center
[IMMIGRANTS crying]

00:21:10.228 --> 00:21:13.523 position:50% align:center
[MIO] I remember something
Chief told me once.

00:21:13.606 --> 00:21:16.443 position:50% align:center
He said hummingbirds
don't connect us to God.

00:21:16.526 --> 00:21:19.946 position:50% align:center
They connect us to our homeland.

00:21:20.030 --> 00:21:22.407 position:50% align:center
And whenever we lose
our way in life,

00:21:22.490 --> 00:21:24.451 position:50% align:center
they'll be there to remind us

00:21:24.534 --> 00:21:28.872 position:50% align:center
that we always have
someplace to go home to.

00:21:28.955 --> 00:21:32.917 position:50% align:center
Chief's Gear is a symbol of all
the things he believed in.

00:21:33.001 --> 00:21:35.879 position:50% align:center
That's why we think it
belongs with you.

00:21:37.422 --> 00:21:41.176 position:50% align:center
[MIO] Mom said she wanted us
to hold onto his gloves.

00:21:41.259 --> 00:21:42.469 position:50% align:center
We want you to take this part

00:21:42.552 --> 00:21:44.804 position:50% align:center
of Chief's legacy
out into the world,

00:21:44.888 --> 00:21:47.640 position:50% align:center
and I'll do my part here,
taking care of his home,

00:21:47.724 --> 00:21:49.642 position:50% align:center
the way he would.

00:21:52.645 --> 00:21:54.564 position:50% align:center
I'll keep it close.

00:21:54.647 --> 00:21:56.816 position:50% align:center
[MARA]
<i>Mi casa es su casa.</i>

00:21:56.900 --> 00:21:58.109 position:50% align:center
I just got off the phone.

00:21:58.193 --> 00:22:00.445 position:50% align:center
We're now the legal
owners of this land.

00:22:00.528 --> 00:22:03.323 position:50% align:center
He did it. Chief actually
made this happen for us.

00:22:03.406 --> 00:22:06.242 position:50% align:center
Yeah! I'm gonna go
spread the news!

00:22:11.706 --> 00:22:13.833 position:50% align:center
[KIDS]
Ready, and...

00:22:16.461 --> 00:22:18.380 position:50% align:center
[MARA]
So what's next for you?

00:22:18.463 --> 00:22:20.924 position:50% align:center
You know you'll always
be welcome here.

00:22:23.051 --> 00:22:26.179 position:50% align:center
[JOE] I still have a
place to go back to.

00:22:26.262 --> 00:22:30.684 position:50% align:center
And I promised him.
No more running.